title: 19 Queuing Theory
dc:creator: mad hat pod
description: Join us in a discussion about queueing theory with guests Professor Jamol Pender and PhD candidate Sophia Novitzky as we discuss how to navigate common areas of lining up and how you might navigate it for the optimal personal result.
